@startuml
title Cognee Production Architecture (Multiple Existing Agents)

left to right direction
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

actor "Agent A\n(Customer Support)" as AgentA
actor "Agent B\n(Procurement)" as AgentB
actor "Agent C\n(Internal Coding)" as AgentC

cloud "Agent Runtime Layer" {
  component "Agent Orchestrator /\nTool Router (ADK/LangGraph/etc.)" as Orchestrator
}

AgentA --> Orchestrator : User tasks
AgentB --> Orchestrator : User tasks
AgentC --> Orchestrator : User tasks

node "Production Cluster (Kubernetes / VM Autoscaling Group)" {
  component "API Gateway / Ingress" as Ingress

  package "Cognee Service" {
    component "Cognee API\n(search/add/cognify/memify)" as CogneeAPI
    queue "Job Queue" as Queue
    component "Worker Pool\n(ingestion + cognify + memify)" as Workers
  }
}

Orchestrator --> Ingress : Tool calls
Ingress --> CogneeAPI : HTTP API

Orchestrator --> CogneeAPI : memory_search()
Orchestrator --> CogneeAPI : memory_write()
Orchestrator --> CogneeAPI : memory_refresh()

database "Relational DB\n(Postgres)" as RelDB
database "Vector DB\n(PGVector / Qdrant / Weaviate)" as VecDB
database "Graph DB\n(Neo4j / Kuzu / Neptune)" as GraphDB
folder "Object Storage\n(S3/GCS/Azure Blob)" as ObjStore

cloud "LLM / Embedding Providers" as ModelProviders
cloud "Business Data Sources\n(Docs, DB exports, logs,\nconversations, tickets)" as Sources
cloud "Observability\n(Logs / Metrics / Traces)" as Obs

Sources --> CogneeAPI : add() data
CogneeAPI --> Queue : enqueue pipeline jobs
Queue --> Workers : async processing

Workers --> ModelProviders : extraction + summaries + embeddings
Workers --> RelDB : metadata / dataset state
Workers --> VecDB : embeddings index
Workers --> GraphDB : entities + relationships
Workers --> ObjStore : raw files / processed artifacts

CogneeAPI --> RelDB : auth, datasets, run state
CogneeAPI --> VecDB : similarity retrieval
CogneeAPI --> GraphDB : graph traversal
CogneeAPI --> ModelProviders : completion (when needed)

CogneeAPI --> Obs : telemetry
Workers --> Obs : pipeline metrics/logs
Ingress --> Obs : request metrics

Orchestrator <-- CogneeAPI : retrieved context + answers
Orchestrator --> AgentA : grounded response
Orchestrator --> AgentB : grounded response
Orchestrator --> AgentC : grounded response

note bottom of CogneeAPI
Cognee is the memory service layer.
Databases are backing stores selected per environment.
end note

@enduml
